e=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Several Switch 2s forming a circle\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Several Switch 2s forming a circle\" data-chomp-id=\"77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e\" data-format=\"png\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Several Switch 2s forming a circle\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Nintendo / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://77d1f4a1296eec052f7caa6fb426f19e\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Several Switch 2s forming a circle\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter Nintendo held its big \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-nintendo-direct-mario-donkey-kong-1851774194\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-nintendo-direct-mario-donkey-kong-1851774194\"\u003eSwitch 2 Direct showcase\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e on April 2, press and content creators around the world had a chance to put the new console through its paces. Attendees were able to play multiple games, including Nintendo’s first-party offerings like \u003cem\u003eMario Kart World\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eMetroid Prime 4: Beyond\u003c/em\u003e, as well as big third-party ports like \u003cem\u003eCyberpunk 2077 \u003c/em\u003eand \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e. From the sound of it, the Switch 2 is exactly what it looks like: a bigger, better version of one of the best video game consoles of all time. - Kenneth Shepard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-hands-on-previews-mouse-mario-kart-1851774555\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-hands-on-previews-mouse-mario-kart-1851774555\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5\" data-recommend-id=\"image://78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Cleaning a teapot house with a pressure washer.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Cleaning a teapot house with a pressure washer.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Cleaning a teapot house with a pressure washer.\" data-chomp-id=\"78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Cleaning a teapot house with a pressure washer.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: FuturLab\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5\" data-recommend-id=\"image://78f81f7024519968ab89258b069c94c5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Cleaning a teapot house with a pressure washer.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eI absolutely adore \u003cem\u003ePowerWash Simulator\u003c/em\u003e. I’ve adored it for three years now. It’s the console game I keep coming back to; curling up on the couch, putting on a podcast, and cleaning the muck off an ice rink or UFO. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-futurlab-square-enix-covid-therapy-1849326953\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-futurlab-square-enix-covid-therapy-1849326953\"\u003eIt got me through a horrible bout of covid\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, it offers me comfort when I’m feeling down, and \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-warhammer-40k-dlc-square-enix-1851268965\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-warhammer-40k-dlc-square-enix-1851268965\"\u003eit keeps adding increasingly peculiar and excellent DLC\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Please, you have to know, I \u003cem\u003elove \u003c/em\u003ethis game. So now, here’s everything wrong with it that I desperately hope to see fixed in the forthcoming sequel. - John Walker \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-2-dlc-clean-dirt-futurlab-1851773438\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/powerwash-simulator-2-dlc-clean-dirt-futurlab-1851773438\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9\" data-recommend-id=\"image://0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Image for article titled The Internet Reacts To The Switch 2 Price And Falls In Love With A Mario Kart World Cow As Last Of Us Discourse Revs Up Once Again\" data-chomp-id=\"0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled The Internet Reacts To The Switch 2 Price And Falls In Love With A Mario Kart World Cow As Last Of Us Discourse Revs Up Once Again\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Nintendo / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9\" data-recommend-id=\"image://0bc58989d2a4a853680360fa226b3fc9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eToday, during \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-nintendo-direct-mario-donkey-kong-1851774194\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-nintendo-direct-mario-donkey-kong-1851774194\"\u003eNintendo’s big Switch 2 Direct\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, we got a bunch of trailers for upcoming games and finally learned that the new console will be launching June 5. But the real star of the show wasn’t a new Donkey Kong game or voice chat, it was a simple yet badass cow on a scooter built out of a boombox.  - Zack Zwiezen \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-moo-moo-meadows-cow-meme-switch-2-1851774370\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-moo-moo-meadows-cow-meme-switch-2-1851774370\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950\" data-recommend-id=\"image://de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Nintendo Switch 2 next to the Switch 2 Camera.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Nintendo Switch 2 next to the Switch 2 Camera.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The Nintendo Switch 2 next to the Switch 2 Camera.\" data-chomp-id=\"de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"The Nintendo Switch 2 next to the Switch 2 Camera.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Nintendo / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950\" data-recommend-id=\"image://de243752c19e204f4ffdf5fb768cb950\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Nintendo Switch 2 next to the Switch 2 Camera.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBack in January, \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-joy-con-nintendo-new-features-1851735307\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-joy-con-nintendo-new-features-1851735307\"\u003eI lamented the idea that the Switch 2 would simply be an upgraded Switch\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Not because I wouldn’t buy one—I’d be there day one regardless—but because what I’ve loved about Nintendo for so many decades is the company’s desire to just be strange. From the clamshell two-screen bizarreness of the DS to the out-of-nowhere stick-waving delight of the Wii, you could count on Nintendo to make things a bit odd. It didn’t look like that was happening at all this year...until the reveal of the camera. - John Walker \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-camera-direct-screen-sharing-1851774311\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-camera-direct-screen-sharing-1851774311\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1565\" data-height=\"880\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Ace stands in the middle of a flooded bathroom, surrounded by toilets.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Ace stands in the middle of a flooded bathroom, surrounded by toilets.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Ace stands in the middle of a flooded bathroom, surrounded by toilets.\" data-chomp-id=\"a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"880\" data-alt=\"Ace stands in the middle of a flooded bathroom, surrounded by toilets.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Guys From Andromeda / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a4a6ae4953497b4f959ed79ea385085a\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1565\" data-height=\"880\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Ace stands in the middle of a flooded bathroom, surrounded by toilets.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e In 2012, renowned developers Scott Murphy and Mark Crowe launched a Kickstarter to spiritually revive their classic \u003cem\u003eSpace Quest\u003c/em\u003e series, a game to be called \u003cem\u003eSpaceVenture\u003c/em\u003e. Some 13 years later, following numerous delays and botched half-launches, the 